notesStmt.note: This conversation takes place over dinner at an international summer school. There are five speakers at the table, and once they are briefly joined by a waitress. The conversation happens in a large dining hall; therefore there is a lot of loud background noise which makes some utterances unintelligible on the recording and sometimes also makes it difficult for the speakers to understand each other across the table. The speakers talk about a number of different topics such as leisure activities like trips to Austrian cities, getting an international student card and the tutorials for their German courses.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
